{"tid":237023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於港大殺數學/物理及天文學Faculty Board Meeting消息","createTime":"2017-05-10T06:09:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-10T06:42:23.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"52fe1667c65f171a4318848185ee98a867c4a22c","tid":237023,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:09:52.000Z","msg":"[關於港大殺科Faculty Board Meeting消息]<br />\n我收到理學員職員消息，希望我能分享下文：<br />\n今日 9/5 開 Science Faculty Board<br />\n傾取消 Math/Phy 同 Astronomy major<br />\n個主席勁唔中立<br />\n經常講自己意見（佢當然係贊成）<br />\n之後仲想就咁通過就算<br />\n「May I have the Board's approval please」<br />\n好在有人大聲 say no<br />\n然後有人要求不記名表決<br />\n拗左好耐終於決定記名表決<br />\n但個決定係主席自己決定<br />\n有人質疑 voting procedures，主席話 rules 無規定<br />\n投票結果係 38:32 通過取消<br />\n如果不記名表決，結果好可能會唔同<br />\n因為好多「建制派」（主要係啲高層）而家被迫支持<br />\n未公佈數字時個主席仲話「it is very clear」<br />\n想就咁當通過<br />\n結果數出嚟係咁近<br />\n個主席真係好離譜！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joanna.ko.7796/posts/309529679478489?comment_id=309567116141412&amp;reply_comment_id=309567926141331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoanna.ko.7796%2Fposts%2F309529679478489%3Fcomment_id%3D309567116141412%26reply_comment_id%3D309567926141331&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e731156d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joanna.ko.7796/posts/309529679478489?comment_id=309567116141412&amp;reply_comment_id=309567926141331</a>"},{"pid":"2bbc04303867b957435ef40695d49cddb5673488","tid":237023,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:10:27.000Z","msg":"暫時結果係成功殺科係與投票結果相反"},{"pid":"6ea51b93d90cda77f296eda043fbc331e8e66ea9","tid":237023,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"個course真係咁受歡迎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申當年有擺落japas"},{"pid":"997aabd07893c2a631182d003c3e3f154e3d5c83","tid":237023,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:13:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個course真係咁受歡迎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申當年有擺落japas</blockquote><br />\n對Math/Phy無咩意見<br />\n殺Astro就麻麻啦"},{"pid":"1b2ac8f11e10d23f4eacaa1277c572f10ff41bd0","tid":237023,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個course真係咁受歡迎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申當年有擺落japas</blockquote><br />\n對Math/Phy無咩意見<br />\n殺Astro就麻麻啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問心有心讀天文學唔揀kongu啦⋯⋯<br />\n個sci fac頹到"},{"pid":"34148cbe6c63079f79dbb3a06983425ef970150d","tid":237023,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"投票有咩用姐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0598539ead21d76882088c32d603726ffa55212","tid":237023,"uid":59181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:21:16.000Z","msg":"其實取消都岩既 香港有邊個會去讀 又唔係搵錢神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b693285b4092071fc3ad5173b4fab1356ea350c7","tid":237023,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實取消都岩既 香港有邊個會去讀 又唔係搵錢神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人讀，但d人去曬CU UST 都唔揀HKU science"},{"pid":"fa2e2a8e7a4dbf013a8cf938852814d6df4f641b","tid":237023,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T06:41:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實取消都岩既 香港有邊個會去讀 又唔係搵錢神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人讀，但d人去曬CU UST 都唔揀HKU science</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhku 理科真係唔得<br />\n最初仲要整個6901谷收生<br />\n而家又係死<br />\n<br />\n搞天文咪又係gimmic野"},{"pid":"26dc